Subject: CAP Not Detecting Correctly
Description: CAP is not working as expected. I'm uploading a test spreadsheet with hundreds of fake SSN numbers to dlptest.com and its not appearing in the CAP logs. This used to work fine, and no changes were recently made to the CAP policies.
What_We_Know__c:
The issue is only reproducible on one mac. All the others work correctly.
We narrowed it to the SWG they are using, and I have asked the client team if there is a known issue with it.
Next_Steps__c: waiting for more test to be made by the customer and an answer from the client team, then I will set a meeting
Solution_Comment__c: the customer changed settings in their VPN software and everything worked.
